p: To the Hon J.R. Lewis Judge within named - respectfully return is the to the requirements of this writ that that \ that I hold here within named Peter Nelson W Smith H Elsner C Whaley G Mattson Charles Lundblad Dennnis Coffy and Jacob Anner in my custody as Deputy Marshal of the United States for the Territory of Washington by virtue of a committment issued to me by D.S.Smith at commissioner for said District and Territory a copy of which said commandment showing his cause of said restraint is hereby annexed marked exhibit "A" and made a part of this return and I also here have the leader of said prisoners before
